{"tid":1822981,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"三大股王幾時會支爆","createTime":"2020-01-13T10:02:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-13T15:41:03.000Z","uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4c26ff03a185ac7281e4a50a05689e273b4eb3e4","tid":1822981,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T10:02:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S18MCai.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS18MCai.jpg&h=2af3e8f2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"db2cb1575293f544dde348a0c34ee52004411d53","tid":1822981,"uid":35930,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T10:04:10.000Z","msg":"點會爆<br />\n<br />\n經濟一片欣欣向榮<br />\n<br />\n仲有十四億人民支持"},{"pid":"ce4caf601bf9d8a793dfc10a310f7b59d8dfd37f","tid":1822981,"uid":252877,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T10:11:02.000Z","msg":"已經爆左，不過係向上爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"737e87be4b1b87732fb89df3780714cd19d38246","tid":1822981,"uid":31925,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T10:12:34.000Z","msg":"【全球8國15市聯手，1.19 天下制裁大遊行！】<br />\n<br />\n攬炒團隊 同各國組織將會喺1.19同步發起遊行集會，支援 「民間集會團隊」發起嘅 1.19 港島東行《天下制裁大遊行》！<br />\n<br />\n即使面對嚴寒飛雪、史無前例山火，英美澳加紐德比等國居民 經過一個月籌備，仍然繼續聯手捍衛香港。<br />\n<br />\n謹此 懇切呼籲各地港人陸續響應號召，舉辦、參加1.19天下制裁行動，逆流打返起個勢！<br />\n<br />\n已確認1.19名單：<br />\n1. 香港 - 香港島<br />\n2. 美國 - 波士頓、洛杉磯、華盛頓特區、三藩市<br />\n3. 德國 - 柏林<br />\n4. 英國 - 倫敦、格拉斯哥<br />\n5.  澳洲 - 布里斯本 、墨爾本、悉民<br />\n6. 紐西蘭 - 奧克蘭、基督城<br />\n7. 比利時 - 布魯塞爾<br />\n8. 加拿大 - 溫哥華<br />\n<br />\n至於各地詳情，請留意 &ldquo;Fight for Freedom. Stand with Hong Kong.&rdquo; Facebook page持續更新。<br />\n<br />\n最後，民集團隊更會喺黎緊星期日1.12 舉辦《天下制裁集會》為1.19集定氣，打響頭炮。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n🔥正牌攬炒Channel🔥<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/StirFryChannel\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FStirFryChannel&d=EP%2BJfZZVzGvO4DQPpGaiyPDXWQKahOldmH8%2Bpia8yKE%3D&h=c579588e\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/StirFryChannel</a><br />\n<br />\n#國際戰線 #本土戰線 #清算<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5jxAQHO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5jxAQHO.jpg&h=b8c68f74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UpXUmPw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUpXUmPw.jpg&h=8fa26607&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e0856f3413bfe6032f09e9501aea04e35874de7f","tid":1822981,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db2cb1575293f544dde348a0c34ee52004411d53","tid":1822981,"uid":35930,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T10:04:10.000Z","msg":"點會爆<br />\n<br />\n經濟一片欣欣向榮<br />\n<br />\n仲有十四億人民支持"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T15:13:39.000Z","msg":"一人一手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ddedbba9acee7ca983a628a20d637ae50f1a5c8","tid":1822981,"uid":90497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T15:19:30.000Z","msg":"會爆GE 爆升姐"},{"pid":"809d06d1382c18d826c902c5bc6b2e2194c775a0","tid":1822981,"uid":316420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T15:41:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />之前好低放左"}]}